    "text": "Note: \u2191shifted one level up, \u2191\u2191shifted two levels up, \u2193shifted one level down, \u2193\u2193shifted two levels down. *Newly added with the last update Special Note: These warning levels are issued based on the cumulative rainfall received to respective areas and given weather forecast by meteorological department of Sri Lanka",
